title: The Heroes, or Greek Fairy Tales for my Children
creator: Charles Kingsley
description: LibriVox recording of The Heroes, or Greek Fairy Tales for my Children by Charles Kingsley. The Heroes, or Greek Fairy Tales for my Children by Charles Kingsley is a collection of three Greek mythology stories: Perseus, The Argonauts, and Theseus. The author had a great fondness for Greek fairy tales and believed the adventures of the characters would inspire children to achieve higher goals with integrity. (summary by Laura Caldwell) M4B audiobook of complete book For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
